These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, architect, social-worker, accountant
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, egyptian, thai, turkish
1. the egyptian is on the left of the chinese##1
2. the musician is the turkish##1
3. the thai is on the right of the chinese##1
4. the architect is on the left of the turkish##1
5. the accountant is on the left of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Job          | accountant | social-worker | architect | musician   |
| Nationality   | egyptian  | chinese     | thai   | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, cooking, video-games, woodworking
There are 4 different nationalities: german, brazilian, nigerian, australian
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the brazilian##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the nigerian##1
5. the brazilian is on the left of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | video-games | woodworking | cooking | camping    |
| Nationality   | nigerian    | brazilian      | german | australian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, fuchsia, azure, ivory
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, mystery, time-travel
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the person who likes apricot is the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
5. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Color         | apricot | ivory | azure   | fuchsia |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | mystery | time-travel | drama         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, drama, western
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, blue, coral, blood-red
1. the person who likes blue is the person watching western movies##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
4. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
5. the person who likes brown is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | western | disaster | action  | drama      |
| Color         | blue | blood-red   | coral | brown |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, cucumber, kiwi, pineapple
4 different games are played: go, canasta, bridge, poker
1. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
3. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person playing poker##1
4. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | pineapple | kiwi | cucumber | cauliflower |
| Game    | go       | poker | bridge | canasta     |

