.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, pop, hip-hop, d&b
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, goldfish, mouse
1. the fan of pop is on the far right##1
2. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
4. the owner of the fish is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | hip-hop | r&b | pop |
| Pet           | fish      | goldfish | mouse | frog    |

