.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, drama, action, musical
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, mouse, rat
1. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
2. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the far right##1
5. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | action | drama | epic | musical  |
| Pet           | mouse | chinchilla | rat       | ferret |

