.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, milk, sprite
4 different pets are kept: frog, rat, rabbit, goat
1. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
3. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | cola | milk  | hot-chocolate | sprite |
| Pet   | goat | rabbit | rat          | frog    |

