The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, martial-arts, spy, horror
1. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking milk is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | sprite | milk  | hot-chocolate | water |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | spy | horror           | martial-arts   |

