3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the argentine is on the right of the canadian##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Nationality   | canadian | argentine | thai | dutch  |
| Beverage           | cola | tea      | lemonade | hot-chocolate |

