.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, sprite, water
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, skateboard, jet-ski, ship
1. the person driving the ship is the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person drinking sprite is the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage   | sprite | juice  | coffee | water   |
| Transport        | jet-ski | skateboard | ship    | airplane |

