.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, romance, superhero, comedy
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, car, scooter, snowmobile
1. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person driving the car is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person watching comedy movies is the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | superhero | romance | comedy   |
| Transport     | scooter  | boat    | car       | snowmobile |

 